    {
      "id": "48",
      "name": "Skill",
      "components": [
        {
          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Normal Attack</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 1 poin <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/28/15595270/1ce09211f025bf5470682189e0837732_2927238317914207092.png",
                "id": "talent80174",
                "key": "Den of Thunder",
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Den of Thunder"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Skill</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>. Jika target sudah terpengaruh Electro, akan mencuri 1 poin Energy lawan. (Jika Energy Karakter ini sudah penuh, maka Energy yang dicuri akan diberikan ke Karakter berikutnya yang Energy-nya belum penuh)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/28/15595270/3d9907052dade051fb723c64be06d271_2306696445178164398.png",
                "id": "talent92639",
                "key": "Shock of the Enigmatic Abyss",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Shock of the Enigmatic Abyss"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Elemental Burst</span></p><p>Mengakibatkan 3 poin <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>. Jika Energy target tidak lebih dari 1, maka mengakibatkan DMG +2.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/28/15595270/8b908fabd463116287d5e81af7175999_6930910575406270440.png",
                "id": "talent24769",
                "key": "Wild Thunderburst",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "electro"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Wild Thunderburst"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Passive Skill</span></p><p>[Pasif] Saat pertandingan dimulai, Karakter ini memperoleh status <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Electric Rebirth</span>.</p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: #ECE5D8\">Electric Rebirth</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFD780\">Status</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Saat Karakter yang terpengaruh gugur:</span> menghapus efek ini, menyelamatkan Karakter agar <span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">tidak gugur</span>, dan memulihkan HP-nya hingga 4 poin. Setelah efek ini terpicu, Karakter mengakibatkan <span style=\"color: #FFACFF\">Electro DMG</span>+1.</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/28/15595270/594963a560726b1248fca6760ce6a894_4240110969930537414.png",
                "id": "talent23943",
                "key": "Electric Rebirth",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Electric Rebirth"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p>Memberikan Electro dan dapat memicu Reaksi Elemental berikut:</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Overloaded</span>: DMG +2 poin untuk kasus ini, target berganti ke Karakter selanjutnya secara paksa</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Superconduct</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Electro-Charged</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, mengakibatkan 1 Piercing DMG kepada seluruh Karakter lawan selain daripada target</p><p>[<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Electro </span>+ <span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 136)\">Dendro</span>] <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Quicken</span>: DMG +1 poin untuk kasus ini, menciptakan [<span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Catalyzing Field</span>] yang memberikan +1 poin DMG ke 2 kasus Dendro DMG atau Electro DMG berikutnya</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/28/15595270/11ea6117480145a30b7893f1e8bd7115_8615277069767151496.png",
                "id": "talent19985",
                "key": "Electro DMG",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Electro DMG"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Tidak Gugur</span></strong></p><p>Sebagian efek dapat menyelamatkan Karakter agar <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">tidak gugur</span> saat HP Karakter mencapai 0 poin, serta memulihkan Karakter tersebut hingga jumlah HP tertentu.</p><p>Dengan begitu, Karakter tidak akan dianggap telah/pernah <span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">gugur</span>. (Maka, equipment dan status yang dimiliki Karakter tidak akan terhapus, Energy yang dimiliki juga tidak akan terhapus.)</p>",
                "icon_url": "https://act-upload.hoyoverse.com/event-ugc-hoyowiki/2024/10/28/15595270/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_3015106188383554752.png",
                "id": "talent92306",
                "key": "Detail Peraturan",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "talent_imgs": [],
                "title": "Detail Peraturan"
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ]
    },
